XPath (XML Path) ek language hai jo HTML/XML document me elements ko locate karne ke liye use hoti hai.

Selenium me XPath ka use web page ke elements (button, textbox, link, etc.) ko identify karne ke liye kiya jata hai 
taaki automation script un par action perform kar sake.

<input id="username" type="text">
driver.findElement(By.xpath("//input[@id='username']"));

Basic XPath Syntax
//tagname[@attribute='value']
